         <div type="edition">
            <div type="textpart" xml:lang="gez" xml:id="exhortation"><label>Introductory exhortation</label>
               <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit"><ab> በስመ ፡...ንነግረክሙ፡ አኃዊነ፡ ፍቁራን፡ ውሉደ፡ ቤተ፡
                  ክርስቲያን። እግዚአብሔር፡ ይባርክሙ፡ ወያብርህ፡ አዕይንተ፡ አልባቢክሙ፡ ለሰሚዓ፡ ተአምሪሃ፡ ለእግዝእትነ፡ ቅድስት፡
                  ወድንግልት፡ በክልኤ፡ ማርያም። .<foreign xml:lang="en"> In the name of the Father, and of
                     the Son, and of the Holy Spirit, one God. We will tell you, our brothers,
                     children of the church, may God bless you and enlighten the eyes of your
                     hearts to hear the miracles of our Lady Mary, the holy and twofold
                     Virgin... </foreign>
                  </ab>
                  <note>Text taken from <ref type="mss" corresp="ESam003"></ref></note></div>
               
               
               <div type="textpart" subtype="explicit"><ab>  ...ቅድመ፡ ሥዕላ፡ ስግዱ ፡ ሰዘኢሰገደ፡ ላቲ፡ ይደምሰስ፡ እምቅዋሙ። ወኢይትዓወቅ፡ ዝክረ፡ ስሙ። አሜን፡
                     ይቤሉ፡ መላእክተ፡ ሰማይ፡ ኵሎሙ።<foreign xml:lang="en"> ... Prostrate yourself before her image, for the
                        name of the one who did not prostrate himself will be blotted out of
                        existence, and the memorial of his name will not be known. And all the
                        angels of heaven will say: "Amen". </foreign>
                  </ab>
                  <note>Text taken from <ref type="mss" corresp="ESam003"></ref></note></div>
            </div>
            
            
            
            
